- v1.0.2 | Mar 07 2026:

  [Fix] ELOG_AUDIT_FILE expansion in elog_init() changed from ${:-} to ${-}
      so consumers can set ELOG_AUDIT_FILE="" to disable audit logging
  [Fix] elog_logrotate_snippet() respects empty ELOG_AUDIT_FILE (omits from
      rotation config when audit is disabled)
  [New] README: integration guide, configuration profiles, use cases, and
      troubleshooting sections
